About Event

​A One-Day Immersive Experience · Small Group · Beta Edition

​As the year comes to a close, many of us reflect, plan, and reset.
This experience offers a different entry point:

​How have you actually been living this year? Through your roles, reactions, and ways of responding?

​Rather than analyzing or discussing personal stories, this one-day immersive experience invites you to explore the year through experience, action, and presence.
